tourBios.curYrHigh: Finished T6 with two others at the Mainland China Qualifying Tournament in early March at Wolong Lake GC in Liuzhou to secure fully-exempt playing privileges for the entire season. Opened 79-75 but rebounded over his final 36 holes with a 1-under 71-72 effort.

dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the PGA Tour China Serie was 64th in 2015 at the Buick Open.
dyn.dynStats: He ranks T86th in Par 3 Performance on the PGA Tour China Series.
